    + "scan":
        <scan>
            % Siphon Leech - a parasitic lifeform. It bleeds off ship energy.
            % Energy parasite - it latches onto the nearest ship and siphons operating energy. Non-lethal.
            % Lifeform - kill it or outrun it to stop the drain.
